DevOps --> Development + Operations --> Better collaboation between development and operations team --> SDLC Automaiton

Tools
1. Git --> Version Control
2. GitHub --> Source Code Management
3. Maven --> Build the code --> Compile, unit test, package the code to create artifacts --> .jar, .war
4. Docker, Kubernetes --> Micro-Services, Containers, Container Engine --> Docker, Container Orchestration Engine --> Kubernetes (K8s)
5. Terraform --> Infrastrcture as Code
6. Ansible --> Configuration Management Tool
7. Monitoring tools --> Prometheus/Grafana, ELK
8. Jenkins --> Integration tools --> CI/CD pipeline
